710462f-a.title: Manhattan: 10th Avenue - 15th Street
710462f-a.text:
Tenth Avenue, east side, from 15th to 16th Streets, showing
demmolitton of front of National Biscuit Gompany Building
for railroad right of way.
March 16, 1933.
P.L. Sperr,Photographer.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.

710463f-a.title: Manhattan: 10th Avenue - 15th Street
710463f-a.text:
Tenth Avenue, west side, from 15th to 16th Streets, showing one of
the National Biscuit Company buildings, from 14th Street across
the clearing for the elevated structure for the New York Central
tracks.
April 20, 1933.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.

710465f-a.title: Manhattan: 10th Avenue - 15th Street
710465f-a.text:
Tenth Avenue, west side, from 16th to 15th Streets, showing one of
the National Biscuit Company buildings seen from across clearing
for the construction of elevated tracks for the New York Central.
April 20, 1933.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
